this isn't a swim in the kiddy pool this has to be complete. But if you fail 
archangel I will not come for you nor do I want to blamed for this failure is 
that clear after the shield lets you in I'm gone for if your captured it will 
be you own stupidity that lead you to defeat. I'll wait at the sector." 
Tigerhawk exits before Archangel can utter a reprise.  

Tigerhawk enters beastmode walks to the waiting point. "His youth is only 
surpassed by his stupidity and lack of the sense the matrix gave a server 
drone."
